{"tid":1373071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好互屌 不論係勇武定和理非 保持獨立思考最重要","createTime":"2019-07-27T14:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T08:19:12.000Z","uid":200855,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"873bf7bb7e1f20bbd669817c44819080247357f4","tid":1373071,"uid":200855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想講句<br />\n呢次運動最大特點就係冇大台 咁既然冇大台 我地應該點？<br />\n冇錯 就係<span style=\"color: red;\"> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每人都保持獨立思考</span> <br />\n</span>自己帶個腦出去行 自己睇情況自己分析<br />\n咁先將冇大台嘅優勢最大化 二百萬人就有二百萬個腦<br />\n<br />\n咁點樣獨立思考？<br />\n冇錯 就係出去嘅人 自己衡量自己身體狀況 裝備夠唔夠等 再決定走唔走 <br />\n<br />\n而唔係盲目信從前線！<br />\n前線係要尊重 但唔係口號式盲信 屌我負皮我都係咁講！<br />\n咩叫現場做決定？係身處現場嘅每一位為自己做決定 而唔係你隔離嗰個點你就點啊<br />\n<br />\n依加連登好撚多風向撚 郁啲就屌人冷氣軍師 多幾個正評就好易帶到風向<br />\n如果大家冇獨立思考嘅能力 又可以防到幾多次五毛帶風向？<br />\n<br />\n話走嘅未必係冷氣軍師 唔可以係去完喺現場覺得唔對路嘅手足俾意見？<br />\n大家都係擔心前線姐 少一個就少好多 俾個意見姐 <br />\n之前已經分析過 有人認為元朗送頭意義係不大 點解要話走嘅人就係唔知頭唔知路嘅冷氣軍師？<br />\n又話勇武同和理非都重要 唔通早走嘅和理非俾人屈係冷氣軍師 就唔會灰？<br />\n希望大家唔好互屌！要留嘅自己留 要走嘅自己走<br />\n唔好命令式屌人走 亦唔好屌人冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要勸走就po逃生路線<br />\n無限尊重留嘅前線 但亦有人可能真係未準備好 唔想未準備好嘅人白白送頭<br />\n<br />\n今次黑警已經柒左幾鑊 留意返 <br />\n黑警做錯=/=前線做啱 <br />\n唔係話留得越耐就可以谷到黑警柒多幾鑊<br />\n如果黑警犯嘅一個錯係需要多位前線犧牲嘅話 希望各位認真諗諗 <br />\n前線真係好重要好珍貴 少一個好難補返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你無可否認 每次都係有堆人勁早話走 有堆人死要磨爛蓆 <br />\n前線要信但唔係盲跟 自己判斷 提防五毛混入去搞事 雖然目前嚟講次次香港人都好叻分辨到 但唔好掉以輕心 時刻保持獨立思考！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6801db784b1517f6896163939aeda3e940a025e","tid":1373071,"uid":19434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:30:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16c3bb11af33b68e403f6765226a60af6d3f0dfa","tid":1373071,"uid":200855,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"打漏<br />\n支持前線 支持準備好嘅手足留低支援<br />\n但更希望大家係及時一齊走！減少流血<br />\n不磨爛蓆 不自私走 要走一齊走"},{"pid":"e1559ef1f74aba59767c6f6505b8111ca9d95a77","tid":1373071,"uid":139931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:42:31.000Z","msg":"永遠只有和理非屌前線<br />\n前線屌和理非就係分化"},{"pid":"8565ba52387115b50010679ffeb3520114c0cf1d","tid":1373071,"uid":200855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1559ef1f74aba59767c6f6505b8111ca9d95a77","tid":1373071,"uid":139931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:42:31.000Z","msg":"永遠只有和理非屌前線<br />\n前線屌和理非就係分化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:45:05.000Z","msg":"點會呢 不互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6134cde5ce53b83d6718e2153b82d1a4695ae1","tid":1373071,"uid":200855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"仆街 今次明顯係大家唔熟元朗路 好多條前線路<br />\n資訊傳遞失誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d028a06811a183dfcc2108d4b2addc0fa8c34f7","tid":1373071,"uid":54809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:15:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ee30bef884f916ce3323a7ef2300a70afdf56076","tid":1373071,"uid":200855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:40:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43e92e7afdda230665c907be7ef0603ea897d756","tid":1373071,"uid":188804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:56:58.000Z","msg":"大家唔好自己人分化"},{"pid":"4936ad1823dae44d5a5a638ef34008c92ac7af38","tid":1373071,"uid":275787,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:58:55.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n<br />\n眼見熱門好撚多分化指責好燥底好嬲<br />\n頭先直頭想開po<br />\n但係燥得濟講到1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n索性唔開。<br />\n（兼且俾人話完我舊po標題冇建設性對場運動冇幫助好燥。）<br />\n（心諗你紅衛兵？）<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日熱門全部都有講話入夜前走<br />\n咁大佬啊人地唔想前線受傷 唔想累到前線走唔到<br />\n咪一齊走囉<br />\n你既然覺得你冇份共識<br />\n咁可唔可以出句聲啊屌你<br />\n你唔出聲選擇自己留嘅就唔好怪人地走曬啦<br />\n自己對自己做嘅決定負責。<br />\n人地唔係一定要用自己人身安全嚟保護前線㗎<br />\n呢啲先係道德綁架<br />\n話be water同齊上齊落係道德綁架前線嗰啲真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好希望嗰啲係五毛/分化撚<br />\n唔想前線真係怪責走咗嘅人<br />\n咁樣落去場運動點持續落去。<br />\n屌<br />\n真心好嬲<br />\n<br />\n又變發洩sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d57b0b46e821209c0c063438713b3347220dce","tid":1373071,"uid":200855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4936ad1823dae44d5a5a638ef34008c92ac7af38","tid":1373071,"uid":275787,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:58:55.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n<br />\n眼見熱門好撚多分化指責好燥底好嬲<br />\n頭先直頭想開po<br />\n但係燥得濟講到1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n索性唔開。<br />\n（兼且俾人話完我舊po標題冇建設性對場運動冇幫助好燥。）<br />\n（心諗你紅衛兵？）<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日熱門全部都有講話入夜前走<br />\n咁大佬啊人地唔想前線受傷 唔想累到前線走唔到<br />\n咪一齊走囉<br />\n你既然覺得你冇份共識<br />\n咁可唔可以出句聲啊屌你<br />\n你唔出聲選擇自己留嘅就唔好怪人地走曬啦<br />\n自己對自己做嘅決定負責。<br />\n人地唔係一定要用自己人身安全嚟保護前線㗎<br />\n呢啲先係道德綁架<br />\n話be water同齊上齊落係道德綁架前線嗰啲真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好希望嗰啲係五毛/分化撚<br />\n唔想前線真係怪責走咗嘅人<br />\n咁樣落去場運動點持續落去。<br />\n屌<br />\n真心好嬲<br />\n<br />\n又變發洩sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:26:21.000Z","msg":"好撚同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝幫推<br />\n<br />\n你地唔撚出聲 後面嘅點撚柒知？跟住事後又屌？"},{"pid":"9db5b8efe20333ee28cfde2c7daebcfbb0a9154c","tid":1373071,"uid":5737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:18:40.000Z","msg":"真係唔知之後會點<br />\n每次我地出黎都有人比人打到流哂血<br />\n我睇呢d睇到好絕望<br />\n次次我地都係硬食棍<br />\n又唔可以反擊<br />\n我地夠竟幾時先有一次可以反擊到<br />\n我正係睇到我地一方面挨打<br />\n我最痛心就係有一班留守最後果班<br />\n我地就好似賣左佢地730走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地死頂到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人話<br />\n唔係點呀 唔通真係殺狗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當敵人抱住扑/殺死你心態已出動<br />\n我地仲抱住憐憫/同情敵人會受傷會唔會太可笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea179b26fed39db4cb9ff404fe79cace68c5a1ec","tid":1373071,"uid":23968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:37:50.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f3839b23538a21670cebce40e4c774fcf89c46c8","tid":1373071,"uid":200855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:58:34.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fda8e535916a3c55e795aff0df8aefce0aa3f13","tid":1373071,"uid":67655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"認同要有獨立思考"},{"pid":"0db4927ac0c53a6598fa4fd43e4427460937f142","tid":1373071,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:19:12.000Z","msg":"認同！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nbetween 建議大家睇下我啲文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入邊一開始有幾篇文希望大家順序睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抗爭成功第三黃金規則詳解 - Be Water (中）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1362131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1362131</a>"}]}